high_descs: walk straight ahead, and then to the sink on your right
grab the butter knife off of the kitchen counter to the left of the sink
slice up the potato on top of the kitchen counter
place the knife down on the kitchen counter
pick up a potato slice off of the kitchen counter
turn around and walk over to the kitchen stove on the right at the end of the room
place the potato slice in the pan on the bottom left burner
pick the pan up off of the burner
turn around and walk over to the kitchen table on your right
place the pan down on top of the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: place a pan down on the kitchen table with a potato inside of it

high_descs: Walk across the room and turn right at the sink so that you are facing it.
Pick up the butter knife located to the left of the salt on the kitchen counter.
Cut the potato that is behind the salt into slices. .
Place the butter knife back on the counter, beside the salt.
Pick up one of the potato slices previously cut.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, turning right at the stove so that you are facing it.
Place the potato slice in the pan on the front, left, burner.
Remove the pan with the potato slice in it from the stove.
Turn around so that you are standing in between the sink and the dining table but facing the dining table.
Place the pan with the potato inside it, on the table, in the middle, between the pump bottle and the plate.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing sliced potato's on the table.

high_descs: Go to the counter by the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter
Cut the potato on the counter with the knife.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up the potato slice on the counter.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the potato slice in a pot on the left of the stove.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Turn around and go to the small table.
Put the pot on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a potato on the small table.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter to the left of the sink.
Slice up the sweet potato that is on the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the knife on the counter standing up in front of the salt shaker.
Pick up a piece of sliced potato.
Turn around and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the oven.
Place the piece of sliced potato in the metal pot that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pot with the piece of sliced potato in it.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the small white table on your right.
Place the metal pot with the potato slice in it onto the table in between the plate and bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pot a potato slice in it on a white table.

high_descs: Walk to the counter next to the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter
slice the potato next to the sink
pick up a slice of potato
put the knife back on the counter
turn around and carry the slice of potato to the stove
place the slice of potato in the pan on the left side of the stove
pick up the pan from the stove
turn around and carry the pan to the square table with the plate on it
place the pan on the table with the handle pointing at the chair and the tip of the pan on the edge of the plate
anns.task_desc: Cook a slice of potato and serve it on the table.

high_descs: Walk to table, turn right to face counter next to sink.
Pick up knife that is next to potato.
Cut potato in half with knife.
Place knife on top of salt shaker on the counter.
Pick up a middle slice of the potato.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.  Face the stove.
Place potato slice in the pot on the left side of the stove top.
Pick up the pot from the stove that contains the potato, on the left hand side.
Turn around and carry the pot with the potato to the table behind you.
Place the pot on the table, on the edge of the plate.
